<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Lazer
d&uuml;zedi&#351;ini&#328; g&ouml;rkezijileri: 12-15 diopri&yacute;a
&ccedil;enli mi&yacute;opi&yacute;a, 18-45
&yacute;a&#351;.&nbsp;Kataraktany&#328;, keratokony&#328;, dowamly
keselleri&#328; barlygynda bu usul kontrendikedir.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Tutu&#351; amal 10-15
minut dowam ed&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Lukman damjalar bilen anestezi
ge&ccedil;ir&yacute;&auml;r, so&#328;ra lazer korne&yacute;any&#328;
&yacute;okarky gatlagyny b&ouml;l&yacute;&auml;r, dogry &#351;ekil
ber&yacute;&auml;r we &uuml;&yacute;tgedilen flapy &yacute;erine
dak&yacute;ar.&nbsp;D&uuml;w&uuml;rtikd&auml;ki kollagen seb&auml;pli flap
&ccedil;alt birikdiril&yacute;&auml;r we yzyna bejeril&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Islendik amalda
